<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 1/4 (50 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Charge.</em></strong> If the boar moves at least 20 ft. straight toward a target and then hits it with a tusk attack on the same turn, the target takes an extra 3 (1d6) slashing damage. If the target is a creature, it must succeed on a DC 11 Strength saving throw or be knocked prone.</p>

<p><strong><em>Relentless (Recharges after a Short or Long Rest).</em></strong> If the boar takes 7 damage or less that would reduce it to 0 hit points, it is reduced to 1 hit point instead.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Tusk.</em></strong> Weapon Attack: +3 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 4 (1d6 + 1) slashing damage.</p>

